---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Navigating Career Transition Finances | Summit Wealth Advisors" 
  description="Gain clarity on complex executive compensation. We simplify 401k rollovers, stock options, and deferred compensation during a career change."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-4">Clarity for Your Next Ascent.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        A career change brings opportunity and complexity. We simplify the financial decisions so you can focus on your new role.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-brand-neutral">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-lg">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700 space-y-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-primary">Simplifying Complex Compensation</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Executive compensation is more than a salary. It's a complex package of benefits, equity, and future promises. Making the right decisions during a transition is critical to maximizing its value. We provide a clear, simple framework for evaluating your options and taking action.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary">Stock Options: Clarity and Action</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Your stock options are a powerful wealth-building tool, but they come with complex rules and tax implications. We simplify the key decisions:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>When to Exercise:</strong> We'll model the trade-offs between exercising early versus waiting, considering factors like the Alternative Minimum Tax (AMT) for ISOs.</li>
            <li><strong>How to Sell:</strong> We help you create a disciplined selling strategy (e.g., a 10b5-1 plan) to diversify your wealth and manage tax liabilities.</li>
            <li><strong>401(k) Rollovers:</strong> We provide a clear analysis of your rollover options, explaining the simple path to consolidate your old 401(k) without triggering unnecessary taxes or penalties.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Internal Linking -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-neutral border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-center text-primary mb-8">Explore Other Life Transitions</h3>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 text-center">
        <a href="/business-exit" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-semibold">Learn how we simplify a business exit &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/resources" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-semibold">Visit our Client Clarity Center &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
